{"tid":2011524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨衛軍：鄺俊宇昨晚向黨衛軍丟水樽 以涉行為不檢扣查","createTime":"2020-05-11T05:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T02:04:51.000Z","uid":21470,"like":6,"dislike":225,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"f958089a40882a2997c7fdb0f4993aac55d606b6","tid":2011524,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:13:43.000Z","msg":"警方指鄺俊宇昨晚聚集期間向警員丟水樽<br />\n11.05.2020 12:08<br />\n<br />\n旺角昨日再有示威活動，警方在驅散期間，將立法會議員鄺俊宇被警員按在地上，再拘捕帶走。警方指鄺俊宇在人群聚集期間，將一個水樽丟向警員方向，警員於是將他拘捕，他涉嫌在公眾地方行為不檢，現正被扣留調查，案件交由西九龍總區重案組跟進。鄺俊宇報稱不適，送往伊利沙伯醫院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286699&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1286699%26csid%3D261_341&d=jhMTXyFjUfd7nN31cC%2BnyQsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=53157204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1286699&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"fca68d8e425e60e2c79289403fe64c044f6d973b","tid":2011524,"uid":309553,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:14:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">高殺傷力武器</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae4522748a8459c56545aa1d4812241e45a88716","tid":2011524,"uid":320192,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:16:52.000Z","msg":"雪糕筒 Airbnb 自導自演 僭建 冰毒 曲解法律<br />\n警察煩請查埋依個<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691a12c1ca523329318ce746c23dbbad8a112c28","tid":2011524,"uid":103916,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:20:27.000Z","msg":"咁樣水樽係邊度？"},{"pid":"5c85325df5693dff30e57791eb30e92d561a6af0","tid":2011524,"uid":271807,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:22:42.000Z","msg":"好難相信，都要安插個罪名比佢，等拘無正當化"},{"pid":"99b12f4623d061abcca85127ee22781a5f5b836c","tid":2011524,"uid"